AndEntityData.c: This entity returns the result of the logical AND operator applied to all inputs. The number of inputs is dependent on the InputCount property. See #AndEntityData.

AIWaypointsShapeData.c: Link inputs are determined by the array of `Waypoints` defined in the properties of this entity. The name of the link input is determined by `SchematicsNameHash` and will reference that waypoint. Set `WaypointId` to 0x[the first 8 digits of the GUID of the object]. See #WaypointData.
